        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1376361900" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11370372790293672555">P.D. James was a gifted author who happened to create complex mysteries. I&apos;m working my way through all of the Adam Dalgliesh series. Many of them are set in either Suffolk or Norfolk. Her characterizations are splendid. Dalgliesh is a noted poet as well as the best detective at Scotland Yard. <br/>This one had to do with rural natives and the people from the new nuclear energy plant on the shore near them. Extremely great mystery! Dense with setting and unique characters.</span>
  <span id="freeText11370372790293672555" style="display:none">P.D. James was a gifted author who happened to create complex mysteries. I'm working my way through all of the Adam Dalgliesh series. Many of them are set in either Suffolk or Norfolk. Her characterizations are splendid. Dalgliesh is a noted poet as well as the best detective at Scotland Yard. <br />This one had to do with rural natives and the people from the new nuclear energy plant on the shore near them. Extremely great mystery! Dense with setting and unique characters.</span>
